			<div id="post-7111" class="post-7111 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-survival-preparedness tag-competitive-shooting tag-firearms tag-firearms-training tag-guns tag-interviews tag-mike-hughes tag-sirt">
			<h2 class="entry-title"><a href="http://www.thesurvivalpodcast.com/hughes-on-self-diagnostic-firearms-training" title="Permalink to Episode-956- Mike Hughes on High Volume, Self Diagnostic Firearms Training" rel="bookmark">Episode-956- Mike Hughes on High Volume, Self Diagnostic Firearms Training</a></h2>

			<div class="entry-meta">
				 <span class="meta-prep meta-prep-author">Posted on</span> <a href="http://www.thesurvivalpodcast.com/hughes-on-self-diagnostic-firearms-training" title="7:51 am" rel="bookmark"><span class="entry-date">August 9, 2012</span></a> <span class="byline"><span class="meta-sep">by</span> <span class="author vcard"><a class="url fn n" href="http://www.thesurvivalpodcast.com/author/Modern Survival" title="View all posts by Modern Survival">Modern Survival</a></span></span><span class="comments-link"><span class="meta-sep">|</span> <a href="http://www.thesurvivalpodcast.com/hughes-on-self-diagnostic-firearms-training#comments" title="Comment on Episode-956- Mike Hughes on High Volume, Self Diagnostic Firearms Training">13 Comments</a></span>
			</div><!-- .entry-meta -->

				<div class="entry-content">
				<div id="tweetbutton7111" class="tw_button" style="float:right;margin-left:10px;"><a href="http://twitter.com/share?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.thesurvivalpodcast.com%2Fhughes-on-self-diagnostic-firearms-training&amp;text=Episode-956-%20Mike%20Hughes%20on%20High%20Volume%2C%20Self%20Diagnostic%20Firearms%20Training&amp;related=&amp;lang=en&amp;count=horizontal&amp;counturl=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.thesurvivalpodcast.com%2Fhughes-on-self-diagnostic-firearms-training" class="twitter-share-button"  style="width:55px;height:22px;background:transparent url('http://www.thesurvivalpodcast.com/wp-content/plugins/wp-tweet-button/tweetn.png') no-repeat  0 0;text-align:left;text-indent:-9999px;display:block;">Tweet</a></div><div class="podPress_content podPress_content_audio_mp3">
<div class="podpress_playerspace podpress_playerspace_audio_mp3 podpress_mp3player" style="display:block;" ><div id="podPressPlayerSpace_5"><!-- podPress --></div></div>
<div class="podPress_downloadlinks podPress_downloadlinks_audio_mp3"><a href="http://www.survivalpodcast.net/audio/2012/8-12/epi-00956-mike-hughes-high-volume-self-diagonistic-training.mp3" target="new" title="Download: Episode-956- Mike Hughes on High Volume, Self Diagnostic Firearms Training" class="podpress_downloadimglink podpress_downloadimglink_audio_mp3"><img src="http://www.thesurvivalpodcast.com/wp-content/plugins/podpress/images/audio_mp3_button.png" class="podPress_imgicon podpress_imgicon_audio_mp3" alt="" /></a> <span class="podpress_mediafile_title podpress_mediafile_title_audio_mp3">Episode-956- Mike Hughes on High Volume, Self Diagnostic Firearms Training</span> <span class="podpress_mediafile_dursize podpress_mediafile_dursize_audio_mp3">[ 1:09:35 ]</span> <a href="#podPressPlayerSpace_5" class="podpress_playlink podpress_playlink_audio_mp3" onclick="javascript:podPressShowHidePlayer('5', 'http://www.survivalpodcast.net/audio/2012/8-12/epi-00956-mike-hughes-high-volume-self-diagonistic-training.mp3', 290, 24, 'false', 'http://www.thesurvivalpodcast.com/wp-content/plugins/podpress/images/vpreview_center.png', 'Episode-956- Mike Hughes on High Volume, Self Diagnostic Firearms Training', 'The Survival Podcast'); return false;"><span id="podPressPlayerSpace_5_PlayLink" class="podPress_playerspace_playlink">Play Now</span></a><input type="hidden" id="podPressPlayerSpace_5_OrigURL" value="http://www.survivalpodcast.net/audio/2012/8-12/epi-00956-mike-hughes-high-volume-self-diagonistic-training.mp3" /> | <a href="#podPressPlayerSpace_5" class="podpress_playinpopup podpress_playinpopup_audio_mp3" onclick="javascript:podPressPopupPlayer('5', 'http://www.survivalpodcast.net/audio/2012/8-12/epi-00956-mike-hughes-high-volume-self-diagonistic-training.mp3', 290, 24, 'The Survival Podcast', '7111', 'Episode-956- Mike Hughes on High Volume, Self Diagnostic Firearms Training', 'The Survival Podcast'); return false;">Play in Popup</a> | <a href="http://www.survivalp