			<div id="post-5320" class="post-5320 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-survival-preparedness tag-civil-unrest tag-firearms tag-frank-sharpe-jr tag-home-defense tag-rifle tag-self-defense tag-shotgun">
			<h2 class="entry-title"><a href="http://www.thesurvivalpodcast.com/frank-sharpe-on-coming-unrest-and-home-defense" title="Permalink to Episode-758- Frank Sharpe on Coming Unrest and Home Defense" rel="bookmark">Episode-758- Frank Sharpe on Coming Unrest and Home Defense</a></h2>

			<div class="entry-meta">
				 <span class="meta-prep meta-prep-author">Posted on</span> <a href="http://www.thesurvivalpodcast.com/frank-sharpe-on-coming-unrest-and-home-defense" title="7:00 am" rel="bookmark"><span class="entry-date">October 7, 2011</span></a> <span class="byline"><span class="meta-sep">by</span> <span class="author vcard"><a class="url fn n" href="http://www.thesurvivalpodcast.com/author/Modern Survival" title="View all posts by Modern Survival">Modern Survival</a></span></span><span class="comments-link"><span class="meta-sep">|</span> <a href="http://www.thesurvivalpodcast.com/frank-sharpe-on-coming-unrest-and-home-defense#comments" title="Comment on Episode-758- Frank Sharpe on Coming Unrest and Home Defense">23 Comments</a></span>
